title: ***Open For Tours On Weekends - Newly Renovated - Endless Amenities***
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
